b'Subarashii Sekai Ryokou: Alaska no Tab: b'In the near future, Earth is engulfed in a new ice age as snow falls ceaselessly in summer and glaciers advance with uncharacteristic speed. In this SF spinoff of the live-action Wonderful World Travel series, humanity must decide whether to use science to fight the ice or to adapt to it. \n\n(Source: Anime Encyclopedia)'
